{
  "stem": "27687.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- well, I didn't actually run away by myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But there was a guy came to the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He must have been about early '30s.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, well, come with us to the forest.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, we work for General Degaulle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we try to be with the-- with the French partisan, with the FFI.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we we're trying to liberate France, and we going to make the Germans a bad time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were just boys.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't even remember the names of my 50 friends what were there with me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember any of these names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only name I remember is Abbai Glazberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Abbai Glazberg, I'd found out when I was there for a while, that he is a Jew.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he is an Abbai.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Abbai means he is some kind of a priest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he is in contact with Degaulle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he is-- he has an intermediary-- what-- a go-between, which was a lady.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she was a refugee from-- from the Communist Party-- from the French Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't remember her name, either.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I only remember Abbai-- Abbai Glazberg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was, you know-- it took me so-- you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- Abbai?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Glazberg?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why I remember his name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I would say that we stayed about-- till about July-- July in 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were surrounded by the French militia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the French fascist party--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they surrounded us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they supposed to deliver us to Lyon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Lyon, there was the Gestapo-- the big Gestapo, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they wanted, probably, to find out more about our work.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
